title: Didn't get the present! :D
body: Well, i read somewhere that the last day for receveing gift is 23.09., today is 24. and i still didnt get mystery skin. But i did get icon. What seems to be the problem? Ty :)

replies.body: The gifts are sent separately so you won't necessarily receive it all at the same time.  We're still sending gifts out and have extended our timeline per the current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  They're coming!

Greetings! 

Getting the gifts out to everyone took a little longer than expected and Riot has announced that they'll try to ship all gifts out by September 30.


- Okuma
